## FileView

Pass in the file from a doctor or user to the props.

```jsx
// file from doctor.file or user.file
let file = {
    "name": "file.pdf",
    "data": "",
    "size": 10182,
    "encoding": "7bit",
    "tempFilePath": "",
    "truncated": false,
    "mimetype": "application/pdf",
    "md5": "5a58e5bc020810ac42fdf7db9cc67fb8"
}


<FileView file={file} />
```
